title: [Cypress Walk, Promenade]
description: Shade provided by carefully tended willows shelters the houses along the cobbled promenade from the sun during daylight hours.  Small gardens of flowers and herbs provide a colorful border between the whitewashed homes and the flow of traffic.

Filtered through carefully tended willows, moonlight dots the cobbled promenade and surrounding homes.  Small gardens of flowers and herbs provide a colorful border between the whitewashed homes and the flow of traffic.
paths: Obvious paths: north, east, south, west
